edu.brown.cs.systems.tracingplane.atom_layer.impl

Class RawAtomLayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.brown.cs.systems.tracingplane.atom_layer.impl.RawAtomLayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AtomLayer<RawBaggageAtoms>, TransitLayer<RawBaggageAtoms>

    public class RawAtomLayer
extends java.lang.Object
implements AtomLayer<RawBaggageAtoms>
    The simple implementation of the context layer that can be used in lieu of a full baggage layer. Simply merges bags lexicographically, removes duplicates, and supports overflow.
